casebody.data:
No. 1109,

October Term, 1968.

Weed v. Bilbrey et al.,

394 U. S. 1018, 395 U. S. 971, 397 U. S. 930. Respondents requested to file response within 30 days to motion for leave to file third petition for rehearing.

The Chief Justice and Mr. Justice Blackmun took no part in the consideration or decision of this matter.
